253
00:18:37,084 --> 00:18:42,008
For many years he had adopted a system ofdocketing all paragraphs concerning men and

254
00:18:42,008 --> 00:18:48,031
things, so that it was difficult to name asubject or a person on which he could not

255
00:18:48,031 --> 00:18:51,018
at once furnish information.

256
00:18:51,018 --> 00:18:55,034
In this case I found her biographysandwiched in between that of a Hebrew

257
00:18:55,034 --> 00:19:00,005
rabbi and that of a staff-commander who hadwritten a monograph upon the deep-sea

258
00:19:00,005 --> 00:19:00,055
fishes.

259
00:19:00,055 --> 00:19:05,139
"Let me see!" said Holmes."Hum!

260
00:19:05,139 --> 00:19:12,499
Born in New Jersey in the year 1858.Contralto--hum!

261
00:19:12,499 --> 00:19:15,034
La Scala, hum!

262
00:19:15,034 --> 00:19:22,072
Prima donna Imperial Opera of Warsaw--yes!Retired from operatic stage--ha!

263
00:19:22,072 --> 00:19:26,008
Living in London--quite so!

264
00:19:26,008 --> 00:19:31,889
Your Majesty, as I understand, becameentangled with this young person, wrote her

265
00:19:31,889 --> 00:19:38,071
some compromising letters, and is nowdesirous of getting those letters back."

266
00:19:38,071 --> 00:19:39,073
"Precisely so.

267
00:19:39,073 --> 00:19:43,129
But how--""Was there a secret marriage?"

268
00:19:43,129 --> 00:19:47,098
"None.""No legal papers or certificates?"

269
00:19:47,098 --> 00:19:49,149
"None."

270
00:19:49,149 --> 00:19:53,097
