271
00:19:53,097 --> 00:19:59,389
letters for blackmailing or other purposes,how is she to prove their authenticity?"

272
00:19:59,389 --> 00:20:03,011
"There is the writing."

273
00:20:03,011 --> 00:20:05,909
"Pooh, pooh!Forgery."

274
00:20:05,909 --> 00:20:08,072
"My private note-paper.""Stolen."

275
00:20:08,072 --> 00:20:12,249
"My own seal."

276
00:20:12,249 --> 00:20:15,649
"Imitated.""My photograph."

277
00:20:15,649 --> 00:20:20,032
"Bought.""We were both in the photograph."

278
00:20:20,032 --> 00:20:21,079
"Oh, dear!

279
00:20:21,079 --> 00:20:25,096
That is very bad!Your Majesty has indeed committed an

280
00:20:25,096 --> 00:20:31,749
indiscretion.""I was mad--insane."

281
00:20:31,749 --> 00:20:35,011
"You have compromised yourself seriously."

282
00:20:35,011 --> 00:20:38,044
"I was only Crown Prince then.I was young.

283
00:20:38,044 --> 00:20:43,061
I am but thirty now.""It must be recovered."

284
00:20:43,061 --> 00:20:46,083
"We have tried and failed."

285
00:20:46,083 --> 00:20:50,057
"Your Majesty must pay.It must be bought."

286
00:20:50,057 --> 00:20:54,048
"She will not sell.""Stolen, then."

287
00:20:54,048 --> 00:20:57,119
"Five attempts have been made.

288
00:20:57,119 --> 00:21:00,068
Twice burglars in my pay ransacked herhouse.

289
00:21:00,068 --> 00:21:03,999
Once we diverted her luggage when shetravelled.

290
00:21:03,999 --> 00:21:05,989
Twice she has been waylaid.

291
00:21:05,989 --> 00:21:09,489
There has been no result.""No sign of it?"

292
00:21:09,489 --> 00:21:15,149
"Absolutely none."Holmes laughed.

293
00:21:15,149 --> 00:21:17,092
"It is quite a pretty little problem," saidhe.

294
00:21:17,092 --> 00:21:25,639
"But a very serious one to me," returnedthe King reproachfully.

295
00:21:25,639 --> 00:21:27,369
"Very, indeed.

296
00:21:27,369 --> 00:21:31,279
And what does she propose to do with thephotograph?"

297
00:21:31,279 --> 00:21:33,082
"To ruin me.""But how?"

298
00:21:33,082 --> 00:21:38,029
"I am about to be married."

299
00:21:38,029 --> 00:21:43,999
"So I have heard.""To Clotilde Lothman von Saxe-Meningen,

300
00:21:43,999 --> 00:21:49,044
second daughter of the King of Scandinavia.You may know the strict principles of her

301
00:21:49,044 --> 00:21:50,619
family.

302
00:21:50,619 --> 00:21:57,017
