303
00:21:57,017 --> 00:22:03,149
bring the matter to an end.""And Irene Adler?"

304
00:22:03,149 --> 00:22:04,083
"Threatens to send them the photograph.

305
00:22:04,083 --> 00:22:09,021
And she will do it.I know that she will do it.

306
00:22:09,021 --> 00:22:13,149
You do not know her, but she has a soul ofsteel.

307
00:22:13,149 --> 00:22:17,098
She has the face of the most beautiful ofwomen, and the mind of the most resolute of

308
00:22:17,098 --> 00:22:19,002
men.

309
00:22:19,002 --> 00:22:23,529
Rather than I should marry another woman,there are no lengths to which she would not

310
00:22:23,529 --> 00:22:28,019
go--none.""You are sure that she has not sent it

311
00:22:28,019 --> 00:22:28,061
yet?"

312
00:22:28,061 --> 00:22:33,029
"I am sure.""And why?"

313
00:22:33,029 --> 00:22:37,889
"Because she has said that she would sendit on the day when the betrothal was

314
00:22:37,889 --> 00:22:39,067
publicly proclaimed.

315
00:22:39,067 --> 00:22:46,017
That will be next Monday.""Oh, then we have three days yet," said

316
00:22:46,017 --> 00:22:47,529
Holmes with a yawn.

317
00:22:47,529 --> 00:22:52,739
"That is very fortunate, as I have one ortwo matters of importance to look into just

318
00:22:52,739 --> 00:22:56,011
at present.Your Majesty will, of course, stay in

319
00:22:56,011 --> 00:22:57,018
London for the present?"

320
00:22:57,018 --> 00:23:02,006
"Certainly.You will find me at the Langham under the

321
00:23:02,006 --> 00:23:07,003
name of the Count Von Kramm.""Then I shall drop you a line to let you

322
00:23:07,003 --> 00:23:09,082
know how we progress."

323
00:23:09,082 --> 00:23:14,033
