439
00:31:21,509 --> 00:31:27,072
"Away they went, and I was just wonderingwhether I should not do well to follow them

440
00:31:27,072 --> 00:31:33,499
when up the lane came a neat little landau,the coachman with his coat only half-

441
00:31:33,499 --> 00:31:36,056
buttoned, and his tie under his ear, while

442
00:31:36,056 --> 00:31:40,399
all the tags of his harness were stickingout of the buckles.

443
00:31:40,399 --> 00:31:44,529
